column2: Hello Kitty x Pusheen Pusheen Jumbo Squishy
column3: So cute, so squishy! These make a great alternative to stress balls for both kids and adults. The Jumbo size clocks in at a 6", perfect for the most satisfying squish . When you're not using it, it makes for a supercute accessory to keep on the shelf or at your desk! PS. It also has a lovely sweet scent! Get both for a matching set! The limited-edition Hello Kitty x Pusheen collaboration unites Hello Kitty and Pusheen® for the first time to celebrate friendship and long-lasting connections! Pusheen is a tubby tabby cat who brings smiles and laughter to people all around the world. She became famous through her animated comics and GIFs, as well as through her widely used animated stickers on Facebook, Instagram, iMessage, and other platforms. ♡ Soft, sweet scent ♡ Slow-rising, super-satisfying squish ♡ Approx. 6"

column2: Badtz-maru Mascot Plush Set (Music Note Series)
column3: Best bros forever! Hana-maru is Badtz-maru's best friend. Even though they might have opposite personalities, that doesn't mean they can't be homies! These clips attach easily to your keys or bag. Leave them together, or give one to your bestie! The Music Note series features Badtz-Maru with his best friend, Hana Maru the seal. Both wear backwards hat and Badtz wears a printed hoodie decorated with boomboxes, record players, and music notes. 🎶 ♡ Music Note Series ♡ Set of 2 ♡ Lobster clasp ♡ Matching outfits ♡ Approx 3.5"
